Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.36,0:00:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.60,0:00:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.72,0:00:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊 突然叫你们出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.30,0:00:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然会被芽间的爸爸反对…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才选这个时间啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.10,0:00:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁叔叔不在的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.46,0:00:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向阿姨进攻!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.57,0:00:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨的话 肯定会站在我们这边的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.84,0:00:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.12,0:00:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都借日记给我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.16,0:00:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是为了芽间 一定会…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.31,0:00:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.18,0:00:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道我们又偷偷地去她家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.12,0:00:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该会生气吧…


Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.42,0:02:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.68,0:02:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 今天集君和知利子也来了么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.89,0:02:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.47,0:02:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.17,0:02:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.27,0:02:20.94,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.13,0:02:21.82,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}抱歉打搅了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.50,0:02:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子会很顺利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.82,0:02:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花火箭…是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.99,0:02:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.35,0:02:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听她爸爸说了 吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.07,0:02:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过不是很好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.89,0:02:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好朋友聚在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起考虑好玩的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.83,0:02:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.78,0:02:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 对的对的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.42,0:02:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候跟芽间说好要一起做的 烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么?  是芽衣子她…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是烟花放成功了 芽间…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣子也…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.64,0:02:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概会高兴吧… 我觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:02:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…想拜托叔叔…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.91,0:03:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的… 你们几个 关系真的是非常好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.17,0:03:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 也说不上非常好…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.93,0:03:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会很羡慕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.78,0:03:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她被同伴排挤了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.11,0:03:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么「芽衣子会高兴」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.02,0:03:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实还是自己在玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打着芽衣子的幌子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿…阿姨…?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.78,0:03:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有没有 我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.07,0:03:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣子她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.19,0:03:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们却…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像什么都没改变似的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.39,0:03:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们和芽衣子一起玩来着吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的日记 看过了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.73,0:03:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间…停下来了啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那个孩子 和过去一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:03:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.66,0:03:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你们可以像这样长大…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.53,0:04:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么只有芽衣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.73,0:04:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有芽衣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.46,0:04:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.59,0:04:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们差不多该告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤见…手没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.56,0:04:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕啊 芽间的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.96,0:04:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可能一直都在怨恨我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人恨到这个份儿上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是我出生以来头一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.45,0:04:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母心吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 父母
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.41,0:04:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「芽间的愿望」什么的 这么荒唐的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该放弃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.67,0:04:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 芽间要怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.92,0:04:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也该发觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是在配合你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.18,0:04:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配合可怜的你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.55,0:05:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也做过那样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不该说别人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.94,0:05:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不会像你一样 把自己的伤痛强加给别人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己的伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.07,0:05:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为你被过去束缚着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.49,0:05:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把芽间的父母都…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.28,0:05:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…全都受到了伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实那是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「受到了伤害」的人… 是雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.78,0:05:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我可是相信的哦 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信芽间是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.96,0:05:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 仁碳?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.43,0:05:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说要大家一起才可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.33,0:05:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以为大家都变了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.82,0:05:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 实际和大家聊了才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实大家并没变很多 真是让我很吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.80,0:05:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.36,0:05:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算再没怎么改变…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的「大家」已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.58,0:06:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,0:06:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…少了一个芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然所谓的「大家」已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我一个人去实现也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.54,0:06:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会一如既往地继续啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.91,0:06:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.01,0:06:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这样很危险吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.77,0:06:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在脱鞋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.19,0:06:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算一个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.13,0:06:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.68,0:06:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算一个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.48,0:06:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你又多做兼职了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…因为体力活挣得比较多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸色好像很不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…因为没睡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.36,0:06:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一直以来都是吃了就睡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡眠攒够了的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么能那么拼命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对芽间就那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.46,0:07:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 仁…仁碳?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这个 营养药
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.87,0:07:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先吃点药吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.27,0:07:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼…好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.65,0:07:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.93,0:07:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再这么做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.74,0:07:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳受的伤害也够多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再这样了 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样是哪样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.43,0:07:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还在工作中呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要你走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.57,0:08:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实不想你走的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.18,0:08:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那时候」是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.00,0:08:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.96,0:08:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在要说些很差劲的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候 其实我松了一口气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳说不喜欢芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.33,0:08:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我很过分 但是真的有点儿开心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你像那样走掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像在说 你最喜欢芽间一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那以后一直很心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没法原谅在那瞬间高兴的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤害了芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又发生那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.22,0:09:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没法…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.63,0:09:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没法原谅喜欢仁碳的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…我…还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.86,0:09:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是要走么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.60,0:09:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪啊 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.19,0:09:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如果 芽间真的在仁碳那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.39,0:09:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现了愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间不就消失了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.38,0:09:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间消失你无所谓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明喜欢她的!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.73,0:09:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.41,0:09:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:09:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这个笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.45,0:10:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在等我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指甲好黑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.51,0:10:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿牙签给你弄干净
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.16,0:10:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 不用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.32,0:10:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要给你弄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果实现了愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间就会…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉 再一下下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那是芽间所希望的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.45,0:10:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.23,0:11:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 那么痛吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:15.94,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗兰德斯的狗：英国童话 讲少年耐罗\N和他的狗帕特拉什的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起「弗兰德斯的狗」的故事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.02,0:11:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕… 帕特拉什的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕特拉什?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.12,0:11:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗兰德斯的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.50,0:11:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前…重播过的那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.30,0:11:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊…这谎撒的太烂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.32,0:11:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得帕特拉什 一定过得很幸福的!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.54,0:11:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为耐罗对它非常非常地好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.45,0:11:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是好朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间

Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:20.01,title_no,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(371,619)}第八集
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:20.01,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(543,706)}I wonder

Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于芽间去世
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.10,0:12:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间的母亲一直憎恨着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.12,0:12:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣一直责备着自己
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.24,0:12:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤见子肯定也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.87,0:12:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算波波也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…都活在罪恶感中无法被救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.35,0:12:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…能够看到芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.52,0:12:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我…被芽间救赎了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.23,0:12:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么的不公平…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.28,0:12:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时间了啊 今天的打工…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.52,0:13:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不 去上学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.65,0:13:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?  你去上学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.71,0:13:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是塔子的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.57,0:13:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去 等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我在下面等咯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我能看到芽间的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.90,0:13:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就有…必须帮芽间实现愿望的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.18,0:13:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生锈了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.27,0:13:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.74,0:13:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.09,0:13:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.24,0:13:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我没有去上学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.44,0:14:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸也一句话都没说过我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.94,0:14:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为他已经受够我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…所谓的父母…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.25,0:14:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 为什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.17,0:14:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 打工的事情 不用放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 原来你知道的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦? 啊 怎么会 你刚才说啥呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 是去本间家的事情?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 什么什么 你说哪个?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.47,0:14:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都知道的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.38,0:14:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都不知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…我连仁太为什么要道歉都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.91,0:14:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:14:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 把香拿过来好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.55,0:15:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真敌不过父母呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.68,0:15:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳居然连早上好都不说就出门了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.95,0:15:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 那是…波波啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.01,0:15:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算芽间的老妈那样对我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.47,0:15:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不可能都让仁碳一个人干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为「超和平Busters」难得恢复了从前的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.75,0:15:30.16,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}喂 波波
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:35.13,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}你们吵架了吗 为什么波波…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我相信芽间的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.28,0:15:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算除了仁碳别人都看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都不相信 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.02,0:15:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 无声电话?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.13,0:16:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…那个 宿海应该在打工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 应该是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.28,0:16:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来电显示是宿海家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海打的…无声电话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得听到一些像沙尘暴一样沙沙的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.22,0:16:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然觉得很傻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.24,0:16:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但说不定 打电话的人并不是宿海…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.03,0:16:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.49,0:16:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.73,0:16:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 安城居然一声不吭就休假
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不希望这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.16,0:16:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有从安城那里听说什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.15,0:16:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 真让人头痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天本来计划和一起去健身的朋友开party的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.41,0:16:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 我该以什么样的表情面对安鸣呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.67,0:16:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.79,0:17:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是 应该道歉的是突然到访的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.89,0:17:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的父母都不太正常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.99,0:17:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个大妈 基本都不出门
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不太愿意见人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我知道 姐姐不在了她也很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 总觉得很不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的母亲是那种人 我都跟着脸红
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在想什么呢…父母们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.43,0:17:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.64,0:17:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我觉得最苦的还是他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.70,0:17:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母 或许…怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.91,0:17:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这些话不该由我说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.53,0:17:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明还有一个活着的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.84,0:17:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.49,0:17:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时我还很小很小
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.20,0:17:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对姐姐基本没什么印象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是有些事情能记起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.11,0:17:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.77,0:18:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.83,0:18:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小聪不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊 姐姐我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是「超和平Busters」哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去保护大家的和平哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.06,0:18:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以小聪要保护我们的家哦 知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.30,0:18:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.53,0:18:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是让我保护家…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.87,0:18:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可那种…小心眼的家庭…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.69,0:18:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安…安城
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.86,0:18:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 仁碳也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:18:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.10,0:19:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 为什么大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…今天去干什么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么…打工…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.42,0:19:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话…你有没打过? 打去我们家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.30,0:19:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五点左右打去我家的 无声电话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无声?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是怎么着 又想说那是芽间干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那个时间我和老爸都不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是芽间…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊你 芽间芽间的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.24,0:19:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 也让我看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,0:19:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间在吧 是的话就让我也看看啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.36,0:19:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手!  雪集!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.14,0:19:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.10,0:19:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.85,0:19:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 冷静一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.91,0:20:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又来!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别再那样说了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太差劲了 宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候还玩芽间的幽灵游戏?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.47,0:20:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.54,0:20:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.88,0:20:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.05,0:20:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在吗 仁碳 芽间在那吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.65,0:20:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也给我停下来 波波
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.87,0:20:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 稍微暂停一下哈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.61,0:20:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.94,0:20:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.66,0:20:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别…再这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.19,0:20:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们对芽间做的事 永远都无法改变
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.18,0:20:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间会道歉什么的都是谎话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.06,0:21:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说芽间会原谅我们…绝对不可能!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.01,0:21:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.23,0:21:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日记?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.06,0:21:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为 为什么…明明没有风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别吓人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.64,0:21:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 到底为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.22,0:21:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 波波
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.85,0:21:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「今天和长大了的大家一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.93,0:21:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「在秘密基地…玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.25,0:21:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不可以打架哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.03,0:21:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『超和平Busters』永远都是好朋友」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.24,0:21:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 给我看看!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.23,0:21:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…芽间的字…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.55,0:21:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.73,0:21:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答对了～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.34,0:21:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.31,0:21:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.87,0:22:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是芽间吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.38,0:22:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯…

